@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<p>
    Welcome to our pet adoption platform, where cats and dogs are given the opportunity to find safe and loving homes.
</p>

<p>
    We believe that pets deserve care, safety, and a family that will treat them with kindness and responsibility.
</p>

<h4 class="mt-4">How adoption works</h4>

<p>
    All our rescued pets are properly cared for, vaccinated, and prepared before being placed for adoption.
    To ensure their safety and well-being, we carefully review each application before approval.
</p>

<p><b>Adoption process:</b></p>

<ol>
    <li>Fill out the adoption application form</li>
    <li>Initial review of your application</li>
    <li>Meet the available pets</li>
    <li>Choose your preferred companion</li>
    <li>Final assessment and scheduling</li>
    <li>Pay adoption fee (Cat / Dog varies)</li>
    <li>Bring your new pet home</li>
</ol>

<p class="mt-3">
    Start your journey today and give a rescued pet a second chance at life.
</p>